data.description: Great custom home built in 1998 on almost half an acre in established neighborhood. In-ground Pool with nice patio and storage. Privacy fenced back yard. Fruit trees.  Home is listed as two bedroom but has two bonus rooms that could be converted easily to extra bedrooms. Large attached two car garage.  This property is financeable Seller would consider FHA or VA financing.
data.whatILove: Inground pool and cabana room. Large lot with fruit trees. Great investment for the right person.
